# shadcn/ui

This project uses shadcn/ui for all UI elements. Always prefer shadcn/ui components over custom-built UI.

## Initialization

If shadcn/ui is not yet initialized, run:

```bash
npx shadcn@latest init
```

## Adding Components

If a component is not yet installed, add it before using it:

```bash
npx shadcn@latest add <component-name>
```

Examples:
- `npx shadcn@latest add button`
- `npx shadcn@latest add card`
- `npx shadcn@latest add input`

Components are installed into `src/components/ui/`.
